Experiment 7 
Using E-commerce collection write a query to display reviews summary. 
The program displays a summary of product reviews by counting total reviews 
and calculating average ratings for each product using aggregation operations. 
Create  Database 
use ecommerceDB 
Insert Data 
db.ecommerce.insertMany([ 
{ 
product: "Laptop", 
reviews: [ 
{ user: "A", rating: 5 }, 
{ user: "B", rating: 4 } 
] 
}, 
{ 
product: "Mobile", 
reviews: [ 
{ user: "C", rating: 3 }, 
{ user: "D", rating: 4 }, 
{ user: "E", rating: 5 } 
] 
} 
]) 
Run Reviews Summary Query 
db.ecommerce.aggregate([ 
{ $unwind: "$reviews" }, 
{ 
$group: { 
_id: "$product", 
totalReviews: { $sum: 1 }, 
avgRating: { $avg: "$reviews.rating" } 
} 
} 
]) 
